  "description": {
   "en": "\"I wanted to see him make this kind of face.\" I was a gloomy nerd in high school, and at that time I was entwined with Washizawa Natsuo – my dark past. Now, a few years later, we have reunited and Natsuo asked me out. This is my chance. We'll go out, then I'll break up with him, leaving him in tatters!  \n\n\n---",
   "pl": "\"Chciałem zobaczyć taką minę\" - Suzuki Hiromu w czasach liceum był ofiarą losu. Postanowił to zmienić - zaczął o siebie dbać i znalazł pracę w salonie fryzjerskim. Pewnego razu do jego salonu przychodzi Natsuo jego szkolny kolega, lecz go nie rozpoznaje i prosi o chodzenie. Czy to jego szansa na zemstę?  \n\n\n---\n\nMulti-work series; Suggested reading order:  \n1: [Sabita Yoru Demo Koi wa Sasayaku](https://mangadex.org/title/15200/) - Main Story  \n2: [Azami](https://mangadex.org/title/18394/) - Prequel to Main Story \u0026 Sequels  \n3: [Renai Rubi no Tadashii Furikata](https://mangadex.org/title/13498/) - Sequel #1  \n4: [Narrow Place Collection](https://mangadex.org/title/19857/) - Side story to Sequel #1  \n5: [Hadakeru Kaibutsu](https://mangadex.org/title/17936/) - Sequel #2  \n6: [Sweet Sweet](https://mangadex.org/title/24709/) - Extra Illustrations"
  },
